(Corrects amount of emissions in
first bullet.) EU releases verified emissions data for 2012 on
website.
* Carbon-dioxide discharges fell 1.4%: data show
* Emissions totaled 1.787b tons in 2012 from the 89% of power
stations and factories reporting
* Emissions from aviation were 55m tons in 2012
* Aviation emissions data covers 68% of operators
* EU emissions-trading system 8.7% oversupplied in 2012: New
